 class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"咁m43 全開光圈sharp 過ff 是正常"},{"pid":"ce2dde152bf81e4dd8676d5c604bd66a5554a745","tid":776751,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:00:30.000Z","msg":"if you have to stop a lens down 2 stops on a FF camera to get a sharp photo then you've lost any IQ advantages FF has over 4/3 (and could actually be bit behind), and the huge difference in size and weight becomes an even bigger negative for FF cameras."},{"pid":"cc8c3f940ea636d6c97eb3226e885d23c1f94caa","tid":776751,"uid":191921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:01:54.000Z","msg":"If one uses FF 28mm at f3.5 for a group should, good luck getting everyone in focus, you'd have to stop down to at least f7 and dramatically increase ISO"},{"pid":"194d53117bac9ce60e1c0717f2d83c25ac4cec5c","tid":776751,"uid":188327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:42:37.000Z","msg":"我明呀，不過m43真係唔易用<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/12/224232_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F12%2F224232_fa63fcaedf609188d03a584e59adaa5b.JPG&h=ddad63f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c700bb6f43b22d47630e3282f8147a41d30c95da","tid":776751,"uid":188327,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T14:53:12.000Z","msg":"好多時我自己用都係用m43<br />\n但真係唔會呀其他人買，<br />\n因為會買得自己多數都知點解，<br />\n而且現時Apsc 真係好左好多，<br />\n特別係canon 又平，影出來又唔錯。"},{"pid":"395b684efab2ae1160b9f7f08517d64808712803","tid":776751,"uid":12881,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-12T15:35:36.000Z","msg":"m43 係幾好<br />\n<br />\n但最戇鳩係鏡群兩間廠互片<br />\nkit又十幾枝 tele又十幾枝<br />\n<br />\n洗得一枝就夠啦<br />\n<br />\n真正有市場既定焦又唔出齊佢 戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a95a70491b82dfbbec9a9ef6c8f859a9146e91ab","tid":776751,"uid